backgroundInformationList.description: Withdrawal of Notice of Intention to Designate the Property - 1 Weatherell Street

noticeDescription:
TAKE NOTICE that Council for the City of Toronto intends to withdraw the notice of intention designate the property, including the lands, buildings and structures thereon, known municipally as 1 Weatherell Street under Part IV, Section 29 of the Ontario Heritage Act, R.S.O. 1990, c.O.18, as amended, as a property of cultural heritage value or interest.

 

Further information in respect of the Withdrawal of Notice of Intention to Designate the Property is available from the City of Toronto at:

 

http://app.toronto.ca/tmmis/viewAgendaItemHistory.do?item=2023.CC2.5
